  "markdown": "# Welcome to CreditReports.dk Support Page\n\nYou will find answers to most common questions and problems by following the links below. If you could not find what you were looking for, you can always [contact us](https://creditreports.dk/contact/) and we will get back to you.\n\nThank you for using our Credit Risk Report platform!\n\n![Get started](/assets/wordpress-media/2020/05/started-300x300.png)\n\n##### Get started\n\nFor how to get started with our Credit risk report platform\n\nGet started\n\n![Support portal](/assets/wordpress-media/2020/05/moreinfo-1-300x300.png)\n\n##### Support portal\n\nFor detailed instructions on how to use the system\n\nSupport portal\n\n![Product ](/assets/wordpress-media/2020/05/product-300x300.png)\n\n##### Product\n\nFor more information about our credit risk report platform\n\nProduct information\n\n![Credit risk models](/assets/wordpress-media/2020/05/models-300x300.png)\n\n##### Credit risk models\n\nFor more information about our credit risk models\n\nModel documentation\n\n![FAQ](/assets/wordpress-media/2024/03/faq-1-300x300.png)\n\n##### FAQ\n\nFor details on how we calculate specific variables featured on our platform\n\nFAQ\n\n![Platform tutorials](/assets/wordpress-media/2024/04/platform_tutorials_V2-300x300.png)\n\n##### Platform tutorials\n\nFor both video and text tutorials on how to use our platform\n\nPlatform tutorials"
}
